            % transCost:                spread in pips
            % pips_TP:                  max TP
            % pips_SL:                  max allowed SL
            % stdev_TP:                 stdev(volatility) for calculating TP
            % stdev_SL:                 stdev(volatility) for calculating SL
            % WhatToPlot:               what do you want to plot:
            %                              0: nothing
